\id PHM DIK. Dink Rek.
\h Pilemon
\toc1 Ath칬r c칦 Paulo g칛t Pilemon
\toc2 Pilemon
\toc3 Pil
\mt1 Ath칬r c칦 Paulo g칛t Pilemon
\imt1 W톝팯t nhom
\ip Pilemon aye raan 칢 l톖c kam k톖c c칦 gam gen Kolothia, ku 칢 ye raan akut k톖c c칦 gam, ku 칢 la alony c톖l Onethimuth. Alony k칢n칢 칢c칦 kat t칢n칢 ye. Naw칢n ke la r톖팯m kek Paulo 톢칬n 칢 m톝팯c ku wel Paulo nhom b칦 ya raan c칦 gam. Ath칬r Paulo c칦 g칛t Pilemon 칢 tuc ye rin b칦 Pilemon d톖팯톖팯r kek alu톖nyde Onethimuth, ku lor ke cie w톝팯t ye yen alony c칦 dhuk t칢n칢 ye, ku 칢 w톝팯t c칦 Onethimuth ya w칛m칢nh c칦 gam aya.
\is1 K칛k t톖팯 th칦n
\io1 Mu톖팯th tue콂 1-3
\io1 Al톝톝c t칢n칢 Pilemon 4-7
\io1 B칦 Pilemon k칢 c칦 Onethimuth wu톖팯톖팯c p칛l piny 8-22
\io1 Mu톖팯th ci칢칢n 23-25
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paulo raan c칦 mac 칢 w톝팯t Jethu raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, yen ag칛t ath칬r t칢n칢 w칛m칛칛th 칢 gam yic Timoth칦 ku m칛thda Pilemon raan luui 톢ok,
\v 2 ku nyanak칛ida Apia ku m칛thdan d톝팯t lui ap톝i c칦m칢nda c톖l Arkiputh ku t칢n칢 k톖c c칦 gam 칢 r톖팯m paandu.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Kol 4:17\x*
\v 3 B칦 d톖팯톖팯r ku dh칢칢콂 Nhialic ku B톝팯ny Jethu raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, aa r칢칢r kek we.
\s1 Al톝톝c t칢n칢 Pilemon
\p 
\v 4 W칛m칛칛th c칦 gam Pilemon, na r톖팯톖팯k ak칬lak칬l ke y칦n aya tak r톖팯톖팯kdi톝팯 yic ku l톝톝c Nhialic ri톝nku.
\v 5 Rin 톢톝n 칢 nhi칢rdun nhi톝톝r y칦n k톖c 칢 Nhialic, ku gamdu t칢n칢 B톝팯ny Jethu, pi콂.
\v 6 R톖팯톖팯kki톝팯 칢 l톖n b칦 piath b톝팯톝팯i kamkua buk athi톝톝i cuk y칬k pi톝팯rda yic t칢n칢 Raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c aa deet yic.
\v 7 Nhi톝팯rdu ac칛 c톖l amit pu톖팯u ap톝i ku deet 톢apu톖팯u rin c칦 y칦n k톖c c칦 Nhialic gam nyu톖팯톖팯th apath.
\s1 Paulo aw칦c Onethimuth b칦 kony
\p 
\v 8 K칢ya, rin w톝팯t k칢n칢, al톝팯u ba y칦 y톖팯톖팯k ke 톢a c칦t w칛muuth rin Raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, k칢 wi칢c ba looi,
\v 9 ku rin nhi칢r nhiaar 톢톝n y칦 yen ab칦 톢톝n y칦 thi칢칢c. K칢n칢 aya looi rin 칢 톢톝n Paulo tit nyin Jethu raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c yic, c칦 mac 칢m칢n w톝팯tde.
\v 10 Y칦n al칛콂 rin Onethimuth c칦 j칛l a manhdi톝팯 rin Raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, rin c칦 톢톝n b톝팯n ya wun w톝팯ike w칛칛r m톝팯c 톢a.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Kol 4:9\x*
\v 11 W칛칛r tue콂 ac칦n k칢n ye kony t칢n칢 y칦, ku 칢m칢n ala k칢 l칢u b칦 kony t칢n칢 톢o 톢odhie, y칦칦n ku 톢톝n.
\v 12 Yeen atu톖톖c ci칢칢n t칢n칢 y칦, c톖k al톖n c칦칦 pi칛ndi톝팯 ye w칦c.
\p 
\v 13 Ee nhiaar b칦 l톖팯k r톝팯톝팯r ke 톢톝n t톝팯thin-ny톖톖t, b칦 톢톝n kony nyi톝ndu m칢n칢 l톖팯k m톝c 톢톝n rin pi칬칬c 칢 w톝팯t Nhialic.
\v 14 Ac칛 w칦c ba y칦 n칛k ku톖톖nydi톝팯, aw칦칢c ba k칢du tak 칢 rot. Ac칦n k칢 lu톖톖i ke k톝팯c 칢 gam.
\p 
\v 15 T톝팯d칢, w톝팯t ji칢l Onethimuth t칢n칢 y칦 칢 rin b칦 yen b톝n dhuk b칛k la r칢칢r ke we c칦칦 ben pu톖팯k rin c칦 gamdun a t칬k.
\v 16 Yeen adhuk t칢n칢 y칦 rin 칢 yen alu톖nydu, ku 콂ic l톖n ye yen w칛muuth aya rin c칦 yen gam. Yeen anhiaar ap톝i ku aba nhiaar ap톝id칦t aya ke c칦t alu톖nydu, ku ye w칛muuth rin B칛nyda.
\p 
\v 17 Na luuiku 칢 t칬k, ke y칦 lor Onethimuth c칦t l톖n b칦 y칦n 톢a lor.
\v 18 Na le k칢r톝톝c c칦 lu톖팯i y칦, t톝팯d칢 ke k톖팯ny 칢 w칢칢u, ku w칦c ke ke nyaai ke k칛kki톝팯 yiic.
\v 19 Ee 톢톝n Paulo 톢톝n ag칛t k칢n칢 칢 ci톝톝ndi톝팯. Y칦칦n aba cu톖팯톖팯t. Ku duk nhom m칛r y칦n ac칦 p칦r ak칬lri칢칢c 칢b칢n y칬k 칢 ri톝nki톝팯.
\v 20 Ke y칦n manh ma, loi k칢n칢 apath rin B칛nyda. Ku 칢 w톝팯t ca lim t칢n칢 y칦 ke 톢o c칦t m칦th 칢 tik rin Raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, d톝톝t 톢apu톖팯u.
\v 21 A콂i톝c l톖n b칦 y칦n k칢 ca thi칢칢c t칢n칢 y칦 looi ku k칛ju칢c k톖팯k.
\p 
\v 22 Ku d톝팯t aya, guir t톝팯n an칦칦n t칢n칢 톢a, t톝k ke Nhialic ab칦 r톖팯톖팯kkun pi콂 ku ab칛 c톖l adhuk t칢n칢 we.
\s1 Mu톖팯th ci칢칢n
\p 
\v 23 Epaprath raan c칦 mac kek 톢톝n rin w톝팯t Jethu raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c, ee we mu톖팯톖팯th.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Kol 1:7; 4:12\x*
\v 24 Ku k톖c lui kek 톢a, Marko ku Arithtarkuth ku Demath ku Luka, aa week mu톖팯톖팯th aya.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Lu톖i 12:12, 25; 13:13; 15:37-39; 19:29; 27:2; Kol 4:10, 14; 2Tim 4:10, 11\x*
\p 
\v 25 B칦 dh칢칢콂 B칛nyda Jethu raan c칦 l톖c ku d톖c r칢칢r ke we 칢b칢n.
